@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="mt-4">
    <h2>Community Skills Exchange Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>Last updated: April 2025</p>

    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>The Community Skills Exchange collects the following information to provide our services:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Account information (name, email, location)</li>
        <li>Skills and interests you choose to share</li>
        <li>Communication between members</li>
        <li>Usage data to improve our platform</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Connect community members with complementary skills</li>
        <li>Notify you about relevant skill requests and offerings</li>
        <li>Improve our platform and user experience</li>
        <li>Protect the security of our community</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Information Sharing</h3>
    <p>We only share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>With other community members when you choose to connect</li>
        <li>With service providers who help us operate the platform</li>
        <li>When required by law or to protect rights and safety</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Your Choices</h3>
    <p>You can control your information by:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Updating your profile and privacy settings</li>
        <li>Choosing what skills and availability you share</li>
        <li>Requesting deletion of your account</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at privacy@communityskillsexchange.org.</p>
</div>